name: A Dark Time For The Rebellion (V)
Lore: 'Absolute control wielded by the Emperor enables the Imperial forces to dominate planetary systems before the Rebel Alliance can gain a foothold.',
Text: 'If opponent went first this game, retrieve 1 force when you play this Interrupt. Add or subtract 1 from opponent''s just drawn destiny. OR Activate up to 2 Force. Or take Control into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Until end of turn, battle destiny draws may not be modified or canceled (unless being redrawn).',
